  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/e7e3f79ca7c84c011597b428937f8453.avif?t=1772251805\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras_big/e7e3f79ca7c84c011597b428937f8453.webp?t=1772251805 width=1560 height=878 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pixel Dungeon is a fast-paced, multiplayer social VR adventure where dungeon-crawling action, physics-based combat, and chaos with friends collide.</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏆<strong>A Meta Quest Essential</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recognized in <strong>Meta’s Best of 2025</strong>, Pixel Dungeon stands as a premier title in the <strong>Action and Adventure</strong> categories with <strong>4.8-star rating</strong>. Join a legendary community and see why it’s a Meta Quest must-play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚔️<strong>Squads Up & Dungeon Chaos</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up in <strong>4-player squads</strong> or hang out in <strong>10-player lobbies</strong>！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No Limits</strong>: Full game owners can host their friends—even those who haven't purchased yet—to explore the entire dungeon together!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/ff91504331bff4050afc976ca9f977a9.poster.avif?t=1772251805\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/ff91504331bff4050afc976ca9f977a9.webm?t=1772251805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/ff91504331bff4050afc976ca9f977a9.mp4?t=1772251805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💥<strong>Epic Boss Battles, 2nd Stage Power-Up</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>4 Bosses to Conquer</strong>: Skull King slashes his axe. Ghost Lord shoots bullets that chase you. Fight them!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Second Stage</strong>: Angel becomes a giant eye monster, firing deadly lasers that burn the ground beneath you. God of Time shatters the ground, forcing everyone into a new arena —battles upgrade are so exciting!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/28cd4f75f5952070737fd179706d0e39.poster.avif?t=1772251805\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/28cd4f75f5952070737fd179706d0e39.webm?t=1772251805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/28cd4f75f5952070737fd179706d0e39.mp4?t=1772251805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚔️<strong>Rich Weapons & Heroes</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hack-n-slash </strong>with Katana, claws and bows that feel real. Every hit, block, and strike is based on physics!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BOSS Weapons: </strong>Crush your bosses with legendary gear and feel the power!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/629bae5b501a6551dc36819b57162c92.poster.avif?t=1772251805\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/629bae5b501a6551dc36819b57162c92.webm?t=1772251805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/629bae5b501a6551dc36819b57162c92.mp4?t=1772251805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Heroes</strong>: The Witcher, Black Knight, Bird Man...choose your heroes!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/8cdcd1fbaffa038436dcd46777a9f4a4.poster.avif?t=1772251805\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/8cdcd1fbaffa038436dcd46777a9f4a4.webm?t=1772251805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063750/extras/8cdcd1fbaffa038436dcd46777a9f4a4.mp4?t=1772251805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
